Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's for 11 people...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since\NI made a portion this large.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, do you usually cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yuito sometimes does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The steel bowl should be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The shelters for Sumeragis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me whisk the eggs for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I could spend\Nquiet time like this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create\Na relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone\Nsomewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here\Nand between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now,\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’ll see I’m always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller coaster\Ninside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and\Nthe unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,WAKANA'S RESOLVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Time travel will exert a great amount of strain\Non the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a lot of things from Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,After comparing the data sent by BABE,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned much about the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And about Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Powers can be very handy for things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually like cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can even do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mother, see you at dinner.\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you need to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming more like your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Brother is more like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,People always say I don't look like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean the look. It's the aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Kaito lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two getting along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He is fine.\NBut I wouldn't say we are getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, about your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved me when Togetsu was hunting me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Kaito, he's always wanted\Nto be a politician
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so he could change this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But he and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are both our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,why is Wakana being sent back to her timeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not particularly strong, but I am still\Na wielder of the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't afford to get too careless, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't eliminate the dimension entanglement\Ninside the Kunad Gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the world will be destroyed very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimension entanglement?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the traces of time manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kunad Gate is a dimensional portal formed\Nduring time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And because it resonates\Nwith Yuito and Kasane's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been existing as a distorted form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito from the future said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A time travel via the distorted dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will create dimensional entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Undoing the dimensional entanglement\Nwill eliminate the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you must both enter the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Its inside is a conceptual space where\Nonly users of Red Strings exist subjectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the space with a lot of weird images?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu called it the Chronos Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chronos Terminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A terminal of time flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean that's where timelines diverge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a space only Yuito and\NKasane can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be why we didn't notice it\Neven though we went to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without traveling to that timeline,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a slight touch from the existence\Nof the Red Strings users
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will create entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As for which timelines created the entanglement,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you must search for them yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, we still have to\Nrely on Yuito and Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But after using the Red Strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, we'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you grew up to become a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have no right to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I once abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost lost your life back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember what happened\Nin Togetsu either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had Naomi to keep my company\Nafter I came to Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I should really thank her for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you still consider me your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The dimensional entanglement is like\Nred threads that are entangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to undo the knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back immediately if it gets too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As for my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We will keep Wakana safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you.\N-You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kasane, are you ready?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You must stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine the view of Chronos Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Chronos Terminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will undo the dimensional entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-I think we made it.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are entanglement spots up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to undo this entanglement\Nfrom different timelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the old OSF hospital from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the inside of dimensional entanglement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's use the Red Strings.\N-Yes. That should undo this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not separating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate and continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Kasane.\NYou're the older sister I can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were born first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're of the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka said it was because of your cryosleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't thanked you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you bringing this up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the day I started using my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I got a tiny portion\Nof power from you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain power cannot be shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only alive now because we met that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I decided to join OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is when I say
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you're welcome. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is the last thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Our next target...\N-Suoh, 50 years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the entanglement created\Nwhen I met the future you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Suoh 50 years into the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, I know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you could rewrite history?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean by time travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that create a new\Ndimensional entanglement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean after the Kunad Gate is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you could travel to\Nany timeline you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had done it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm dying anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't answer Nagi's question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you use the Red Strings to go back in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I change the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the future is still full of uncertainties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If Nagi hadn't become my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe he wouldn't have\Ngotten caught up in all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had never met Nagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't pursue the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To change the past over that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is just not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi deserves to have his own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the entanglement,\Nnothing is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing another person's life\Nbased on my opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is just not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for asking that strange question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, I might have\Ngiven a different answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a different view of the world\Nafter meeting everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. It was the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We share quite a lot in common, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start from the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Now, the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you can do it.\NJust a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll support that thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one entanglement left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The crest of Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I saw when I first came in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Mother said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Another entanglement was created
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,when we came into contact\Nwith another power user.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is going to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's do this.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now! It's the overexertion of brain power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we need to be faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've both safe. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we somehow made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Kunad Gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You both did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, we undo the entanglements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made a lot of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This friendship is more precious\Nthan any Red String.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You've become so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, are you going back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, Togetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but staying here with you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,just doesn't seem right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I still have so much to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,May you have a happy life in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mother!\N-Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Another entanglement was created\Nwhen you traveled through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I stay,\Nthe Kunad Gate will continue to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She left a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry this is how I bid you farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have told you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I'll be calm enough\Nto explain everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I must return to my own timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll already be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind when I received\Nthe data from BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I must fulfill my duty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in my own timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I could receive the data from Togetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because they retrieved my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A connection was formed between BABE and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This outcome will surely make you sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I now know my two beloved children
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,have grown up to become so strong and amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have my brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but you cannot take away\Nmy memory of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the two of you can overcome anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that you've come into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being alive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and bringing my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,WARNING, EXECUTING
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,DELETION COMPLETE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the happiness you will have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is so much more than what I received.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,PLAYBACK ENDED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,THE TWO BROTHERS
